296
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:35,319
Yes, the hosts can't be late.

297
00:22:35,319 --> 00:22:36,448
Indeed.

298
00:22:36,448 --> 00:22:38,079
Bao, are you ready yet?

299
00:22:38,079 --> 00:22:40,200
Dad, Mom, do I look good?

300
