- Hello.
- Congratulations.

302
00:22:59,599 --> 00:23:01,759
Everyone, you must have a great time tonight.

303
00:23:01,759 --> 00:23:03,519
They are such a great match.

304
00:23:03,519 --> 00:23:05,240
Hello, hello, hello.

305
00:23:05,240 --> 00:23:06,920
Take a nicer shot, okay?

306
00:23:06,920 --> 00:23:08,599
Okay, you look good.

307
00:23:09,720 --> 00:23:10,799
So beautiful.

308
00:23:10,799 --> 00:23:12,519
Great, nice! Strike another pose.

309
00:23:12,519 --> 00:23:13,600
Cheers.

310
00:23:15,680 --> 00:23:17,279
All the guests have arrived.

311
00:23:17,279 --> 00:23:18,640
Go get ready.

312
00:23:18,640 --> 00:23:20,400
See if your brother is ready.
It's about to start.

313
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:21,799
Hurry up and get ready.

314
00:23:21,799 --> 00:23:22,880
Good morning.

315
00:23:22,880 --> 00:23:24,279
Good morning, Uncle.

316
00:23:24,279 --> 00:23:25,427
Good morning.

317
00:23:25,427 --> 00:23:27,571
<i>[Lounge]</i>

318
00:23:32,720 --> 00:23:34,240
So beautiful!

319
00:23:36,359 --> 00:23:38,000
Happy wedding!

320
00:23:39,319 --> 00:23:40,576
You guys hurry up and get ready.

321
00:23:40,576 --> 00:23:41,680
See you in a bit.

322
00:23:41,680 --> 00:23:43,119
Bye-bye.

323
00:23:46,400 --> 00:23:47,559
Who is it?

324
00:23:47,559 --> 00:23:48,920
It's me, brother. Can I come in?

325
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:53,000
Bearing of a great general.

326
00:23:53,000 --> 00:23:55,440
You seem very nervous today.

327
00:23:55,440 --> 00:23:56,640
What do you think?

328
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:58,519
Wait till you get married
and we'll see how you do.

329
00:23:58,519 --> 00:23:59,680
How so?

330
00:23:59,680 --> 00:24:01,359
A crybaby, for sure.

331
00:24:01,359 --> 00:24:04,640
Well, I will just cry on your shoulder
when the time comes.

332
00:24:06,240 --> 00:24:07,328
Okay, okay.

333
00:24:07,839 --> 00:24:10,160
Okay, how do I look?

334
00:24:10,160 --> 00:24:11,759
Number one in the world.

335
00:24:11,759 --> 00:24:12,928
Handsome.

336
00:24:13,759 --> 00:24:14,960
- I love you
- I love you.

337
00:24:16,512 --> 00:24:17,632
Let's go.

338
00:24:18,240 --> 00:24:19,296
Let's go.

339
00:24:23,079 --> 00:24:24,279
He's coming. He's coming.

340
00:24:29,480 --> 00:24:30,592
Handsome!

341
00:24:31,400 --> 00:24:32,880
What a good-looking guy!

342
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:35,119
So cool.

343
00:24:38,519 --> 00:24:39,776
Hao, congratulations!

344
00:24:39,776 --> 00:24:40,839
Dr. Zhong.

345
00:24:40,839 --> 00:24:42,016
Thank you.

346
00:24:43,136 --> 00:24:45,600
<i>♫ I'm all in ♫</i>

347
00:24:45,600 --> 00:24:47,872
<i>♫ All in ♫</i>

348
00:24:47,872 --> 00:24:50,880
<i>♫ But you just want to have fun ♫</i>

349
00:24:50,880 --> 00:24:53,536
<i>♫ And I'm coming under ♫</i>

350
00:25:00,672 --> 00:25:05,696
<i>♫ For you ♫</i>

351
00:25:05,696 --> 00:25:10,368
<i>♫ If only you knew ♫</i>

352
00:25:12,079 --> 00:25:13,184
That's the bride!

353
00:25:15,559 --> 00:25:16,576
So beautiful!

354
00:25:19,839 --> 00:25:21,200
Here she comes!

355
00:25:21,200 --> 00:25:22,640
Happy wedding.

356
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:25,200
So pretty!

357
00:25:29,720 --> 00:25:31,039
Congratulations!

358
00:25:35,443 --> 00:25:37,856
<i>♫ I'll be with you ♫</i>

359
00:25:40,960 --> 00:25:43,456
<i>♫ I'll be with you ♫</i>

360
00:25:53,240 --> 00:25:54,336
Father.

361
00:25:55,559 --> 00:25:57,720
I will certainly treat Jiajia just like you do.

362
00:25:59,000 --> 00:26:00,192
Trust me.

363
00:26:01,715 --> 00:26:03,488
<i>♫ All in ♫</i>

364
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:25,568
Next up.

365
00:26:26,079 --> 00:26:30,599
Now we will give our time
to the bride and groom.

366
00:26:31,119 --> 00:26:34,279
Yes! Yeah!

367
00:26:34,279 --> 00:26:39,200
Hello everyone, today I'm making
a once-in-a-lifetime speech.

368
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:42,839
So I've prepared for a long time.

369
00:26:43,440 --> 00:26:44,880
So here I go.

370
00:26:48,720 --> 00:26:49,728
Xu Jiajia.

371
00:26:51,599 --> 00:26:55,319
I've always felt that life is a lonely journey.

372
00:26:58,839 --> 00:27:00,279
In this vast world,

373
00:27:01,680 --> 00:27:04,119
the relationships between people are all

374
00:27:04,119 --> 00:27:05,248
temporary.

375
00:27:08,680 --> 00:27:09,880
But then I met you.

376
00:27:12,079 --> 00:27:14,640
When I was very confused, when I

377
00:27:15,920 --> 00:27:18,000
didn't even want to face myself,

378
00:27:19,440 --> 00:27:21,039
you were always there by my side.

379
00:27:23,240 --> 00:27:26,559
In front of you, I have no
concealment and no disguise.

380
00:27:27,920 --> 00:27:31,519
We can be ourselves sincerely.

381
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:36,839
Love actually requires a lot of courage

382
00:27:36,839 --> 00:27:39,599
and a little bit of madness.

383
00:27:40,400 --> 00:27:43,160
Love does not hesitate.

384
00:27:45,680 --> 00:27:46,839
Love does not back down.

385
00:27:48,960 --> 00:27:51,920
So I am very grateful

386
00:27:51,920 --> 00:27:53,359
that at every crossroad

387
00:27:53,359 --> 00:27:55,680
that might change our relationship,

388
00:27:58,400 --> 00:28:00,480
we chose each other without hesitation.

389
00:28:02,119 --> 00:28:03,759
So I really want to thank you.

390
00:28:03,759 --> 00:28:07,519
Thank you for making me as brave as you.

391
00:28:18,440 --> 00:28:19,440
Okay, that's it.

392
00:28:20,519 --> 00:28:21,720
Great!

393
00:28:21,720 --> 00:28:22,752
Well said.

394
00:28:26,880 --> 00:28:28,480
Hao, do you remember that day?

395
00:28:30,079 --> 00:28:32,680
I was leading a tour in Brazil,
and you were working in Macau.

396
00:28:33,799 --> 00:28:36,519
I told you, I really wanted to eat that cake

397
00:28:36,519 --> 00:28:38,440
you took me to eat in Macau.

398
00:28:39,119 --> 00:28:43,240
And this person, with the cake I wanted,

399
00:28:44,279 --> 00:28:47,279
flew across half the world to be by my side.

400
00:28:49,480 --> 00:28:50,559
The cake melted.

401
00:28:52,519 --> 00:28:53,680
And so did I.

402
00:29:02,839 --> 00:29:06,599
You know that what I'm most nervous
about for the wedding is the vows.

403
00:29:07,839 --> 00:29:10,079
I truly revised them over and over again.

404
00:29:10,079 --> 00:29:11,960
One day, I fell asleep while writing them.

405
00:29:13,160 --> 00:29:14,920
When I woke up the next day,

406
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:20,200
I found that he had crossed out what I wrote,

407
00:29:21,039 --> 00:29:23,720
'I will be a good wife',

408
00:29:25,519 --> 00:29:26,839
and he wrote,

409
00:29:28,160 --> 00:29:31,519
'I hope you are not bound
by the identity of a wife,

410
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:36,559
to be forever free, and to always be yourself'.

411
00:29:40,319 --> 00:29:42,799
So today, here, I also want to tell you

412
00:29:42,799 --> 00:29:44,559
that I hope that in love,

413
00:29:46,279 --> 00:29:47,480
you can freely be yourself.

414
00:29:48,799 --> 00:29:51,839
And I will always protect you.

415
00:29:58,119 --> 00:30:01,839
Awesome!

416
00:30:24,992 --> 00:30:26,592
<i>♫ No safety net ♫</i>

417
00:30:26,592 --> 00:30:29,536
<i>♫ Places I've never been ♫</i>

418
00:30:30,144 --> 00:30:31,584
<i>♫ Sinking in steps ♫</i>

419
00:30:31,584 --> 00:30:33,024
<i>♫ Into the depth ♫</i>

420
00:30:36,160 --> 00:30:38,319
Okay, I hereby announce

421
00:30:38,319 --> 00:30:40,759
that Xu Junhao and Xu Jiajia

422
00:30:41,440 --> 00:30:45,000
are now officially pronounced husband and wife.

423
00:30:45,000 --> 00:30:49,536
<i>♫ I want to be a lot of things ♫</i>

424
00:30:55,776 --> 00:30:59,136
<i>♫ I wanna reach it and higher ♫</i>

425
00:30:59,136 --> 00:31:02,400
<i>♫ I can't hold back now ♫</i>

426
00:31:02,400 --> 00:31:05,088
<i>♫ Something's got to change ♫</i>

427
00:31:36,659 --> 00:31:38,400
<i>♫ Run off the edge ♫</i>

428
00:31:38,400 --> 00:31:40,032
<i>♫ No safety net ♫</i>

429
00:31:40,032 --> 00:31:42,592
<i>♫ Places I've never been ♫</i>

430
00:31:43,232 --> 00:31:44,960
<i>♫ Sinking in steps ♫</i>

431
00:31:44,960 --> 00:31:46,272
<i>♫ Into the depth ♫</i>

432
00:32:02,960 --> 00:32:04,039
Would you like to go for a walk together?

433
00:32:05,599 --> 00:32:06,688
Okay.

434
00:32:17,319 --> 00:32:18,319
I am leaving tomorrow.

435
00:32:23,440 --> 00:32:24,608
I know.

436
00:32:29,759 --> 00:32:32,240
I feel like these few days in Macau

437
00:32:33,200 --> 00:32:35,599
are so unreal, like a dream.

438
00:32:38,640 --> 00:32:41,119
Who would have thought in just these few days,

439
00:32:41,119 --> 00:32:42,440
I could meet such a group of people

440
00:32:43,039 --> 00:32:47,240
and on the last day, to attend such a wedding?

441
00:32:49,680 --> 00:32:50,784
Thank you for coming.

442
00:32:55,119 --> 00:32:56,519
I also feel it's so surreal.

443
00:32:58,640 --> 00:33:02,240
It feels like just yesterday, I was helping you
pick up your phone by the fountain.

444
00:33:04,920 --> 00:33:08,480
And yet it also feels like we've known
each other for a very, very long time.

445
00:33:11,279 --> 00:33:12,319
It's quite magical.

446
00:33:30,799 --> 00:33:33,519
I don't want to leave here with regrets.

447
00:33:33,519 --> 00:33:35,160
So I feel there are some things
that still need to be said.

448
00:33:35,160 --> 00:33:36,224
Zhenzhen told me

449
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:40,480
that people need the right timing.

450
00:33:43,839 --> 00:33:48,160
Earlier or later won't work.

451
00:33:50,039 --> 00:33:53,519
About all those things you said
and the concerns you have,

452
00:33:55,519 --> 00:33:56,680
I understand them all.

453
00:33:58,960 --> 00:34:03,119
Perhaps, we both need to have more patience

454
00:34:05,519 --> 00:34:07,319
to wait for our right moment to come.

455
00:34:09,320 --> 00:34:12,960
I believe I will definitely see you again.

456
00:34:15,960 --> 00:34:17,079
And when that time comes,

457
00:34:20,280 --> 00:34:22,000
I won't let you leave.

458
00:34:49,440 --> 00:34:50,960
- Cheers.
- Sure!

459
00:34:50,960 --> 00:34:52,559
- Come on.
- Let's go.

460
00:34:53,639 --> 00:34:54,976
Come on.

461
00:34:54,976 --> 00:34:56,239
Casey.

462
00:34:56,239 --> 00:34:58,760
The racers are checking out consecutively now.

463
00:34:58,760 --> 00:35:00,559
It won't be very busy after this.

464
00:35:00,559 --> 00:35:02,480
You all can finally finish work earlier now.

465
00:35:02,480 --> 00:35:04,599
Casey, stop making fun of me.

466
00:35:04,599 --> 00:35:07,000
You're going to America soon. Take care.

467
00:35:07,800 --> 00:35:08,800
- You too.
- Cheers.

468
00:35:18,039 --> 00:35:19,039
Did he leave too?

469
00:35:21,280 --> 00:35:23,239
I don't know, maybe.

470
00:35:24,159 --> 00:35:25,639
Are you two just going to leave it at that?

471
00:35:26,880 --> 00:35:28,320
Actually, I don't get it.

472
00:35:28,320 --> 00:35:31,119
If there's a misunderstanding,
why not clarify it?

473
00:35:31,119 --> 00:35:32,320
Isn't it quite simple?

474
00:35:33,400 --> 00:35:35,000
I don't know how to say it.

475
00:35:35,000 --> 00:35:36,159
I've already messed it up.

476
00:35:37,440 --> 00:35:38,719
And you know,

477
00:35:39,920 --> 00:35:41,480
my intentions were not pure either.

478
00:35:43,519 --> 00:35:45,000
Actually, our biggest problem now

479
00:35:45,000 --> 00:35:46,599
is that our life rhythms are too different.

480
00:35:47,199 --> 00:35:49,159
Temporarily speaking, neither
can accommodate the other.

481
00:35:51,199 --> 00:35:52,256
Maybe in the future,

482
00:35:54,079 --> 00:35:56,039
if fate allows, we'll meet again.

483
00:35:57,159 --> 00:35:58,240
But not now.

484
00:35:58,920 --> 00:36:01,280
I really think you're overthinking it.

485
00:36:01,280 --> 00:36:04,199
If you love each other, stay together.
If not, then part ways.

486
00:36:04,840 --> 00:36:06,400
You're clearly so in love,

487
00:36:06,400 --> 00:36:08,239
why deny it?

488
00:36:10,360 --> 00:36:11,392
Ladies and gentlemen.

489
00:36:13,039 --> 00:36:15,559
The new father-in-law has
something to say, come on.

490
00:36:16,280 --> 00:36:17,719
Yeah!

491
00:36:17,719 --> 00:36:18,840
Yes!

492
00:36:24,840 --> 00:36:26,679
I'm very grateful to everyone today

493
00:36:27,480 --> 00:36:31,039
for taking the trouble to come
to Hao and Jiajia's wedding,

494
00:36:31,039 --> 00:36:32,280
and together with us,

495
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:35,719
to share the most important day of their lives.

496
00:36:35,719 --> 00:36:39,039
Hao's words earlier moved me deeply.

497
00:36:39,039 --> 00:36:43,000
The most important thing in life
is not the result,

498
00:36:44,079 --> 00:36:45,280
nor the process.

499
00:36:46,639 --> 00:36:47,776
It's the companionship.

500
00:36:51,280 --> 00:36:54,079
It's having someone by your side

501
00:36:55,320 --> 00:36:58,239
right now, at this moment.

502
00:36:58,239 --> 00:37:00,639
Whether it's the person you love,

503
00:37:01,159 --> 00:37:04,440
a friend, or your partner.

504
00:37:05,679 --> 00:37:07,639
Today, this toast

505
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:12,199
is to thank you for your companionship
right now, thank you.

506
00:37:12,736 --> 00:37:13,880
Thank you all.

507
00:37:13,880 --> 00:37:15,039
Thank you.

508
00:37:15,039 --> 00:37:16,119
Come, cheers.

509
00:37:17,696 --> 00:37:18,816
Cheers.

510
00:37:19,320 --> 00:37:20,360
You can really hold your liquor.

511
00:37:22,840 --> 00:37:25,880
I hope everyone has an awesome night.

512
00:37:28,079 --> 00:37:29,239
Mr. Xu said it well.

513
00:37:30,320 --> 00:37:32,599
Then let me say a few words as well.

514
00:37:32,599 --> 00:37:33,760
Okay, come on.

515
00:37:33,760 --> 00:37:34,816
Yeah! Great.

516
00:37:37,320 --> 00:37:39,960
Today, as a man

517
00:37:41,320 --> 00:37:43,840
with some extra marriage experience,

518
00:37:44,760 --> 00:37:47,639
I'd like to share a little tip of mine

519
00:37:47,639 --> 00:37:50,880
with Jiajia and Xu.

520
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:53,320
Love begins with passion

521
00:37:53,320 --> 00:37:55,880
but fails with monotony.

522
00:37:57,480 --> 00:38:03,159
So never stop dating, no matter what.

523
00:38:03,159 --> 00:38:06,039
Good! Great.

524
00:38:06,039 --> 00:38:07,079
Yes, that's right.

525
00:38:07,599 --> 00:38:12,400
Don't get hung up on what's right
or wrong in a marriage.

526
00:38:12,400 --> 00:38:13,840
Because in life,

527
00:38:13,840 --> 00:38:18,239
many things don't have clear-cut answers.

528
00:38:18,239 --> 00:38:20,880
Instead, listen more.

529
00:38:20,880 --> 00:38:22,760
You can act silly.

530
00:38:22,760 --> 00:38:25,119
You can embarrass yourselves
by doing foolish things,

531
00:38:25,119 --> 00:38:27,960
doing things that make the other person laugh.

532
00:38:30,840 --> 00:38:32,280
Hug each other every day.

533
00:38:36,559 --> 00:38:38,280
And finally, I'd like to tell
you one last thing.

534
00:38:39,480 --> 00:38:42,679
Marrying Jiajia today,
you've really hit the jackpot.

535
00:38:42,679 --> 00:38:43,920
Yes, that's true.

536
00:38:44,440 --> 00:38:45,639
If I hear that Jiajia

537
00:38:45,639 --> 00:38:47,519
has been wronged by you here,

538
00:38:48,159 --> 00:38:50,719
it takes only three hours
to fly from Beijing to Macau.

539
00:38:51,840 --> 00:38:55,232
